                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>@Compendium[pf2e.bestiary-ability-glossary-srd.Aura]{Aura} 90 feet, <span data-pf2-check=\"will\" data-pf2-traits=\"aura,emotion,fear,mental\" data-pf2-label=\"Frightening Presence DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"42\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">will</span> save</p>\n<hr />\n<p>A creature that first enters the area must attempt a Will save.<span data-visibility=\"gm\"> Regardless of the result of the saving throw, the creature is temporarily immune to this monster's Frightful Presence for 1 minute.</span></p>\n<div data-visibility=\"gm\">\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected by the presence.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 4}.</p>\n</div>"
