                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The dragonshard guardian takes cold, fire, electricity, or sonic damage from a nonâ€“dragonshard guardian source;</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The dragonshard guardian's body absorbs the energy entirely, preventing the damage from harming the construct. Its body reverberates and transforms the absorbed energy before projecting it outward in a 60-foot burst.</p>\n<p>Each creature within the burst takes an amount of fire damage equal to the amount of energy damage absorbed by the triggering attack, including any damage resisted by the guardian's resistances and additional damage from its weakness (<span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect,arcane,fire\" data-pf2-label=\"Reverberating Revenge DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"45\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save).</p>\n<p>This fire damage doesn't harm objects or constructs.</p>"
